{
  "stem": "4670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there was really no reason for me to be there except her kindness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After a month, we decided we would hang on a little longer, and we asked them for an extension, and they gave us the extension.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They said-- they wrote-- they said we were actually deported, but we would have that month.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The reason that we decided that we would take just the month because we-- at that time, we had already decided we would live there illegally because other refugees were doing the exact same thing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We moved to a town called Diemen, and it was on the outskirts of Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was being run by a mayor and he was corrupt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was taking money on the side, and he didn't ask any questions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's all we cared about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We found a little attic apartment in Diemen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I continued my work, and so did my sisters, and we traveled.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was really beginning to love Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It had never occurred to me it would end at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I would spend Sundays at the Rijksmuseum because I loved art.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Art was always my love.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I'd read about Rembrandt and other artists that I liked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And as far as-- I mean, we had made friends.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And as far as I'm concerned, I was going to be Dutch.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only hitch was the time was going out, and we were staying there much longer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the month went by, and two months, and much more time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was getting to be October and I was a very skinny kid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was always cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was bugging my father for my winter coat because they were in storage.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
